ikaaro 0.62.7 (2011/03/XX)
==========================

This is a Content Management System built on Python & itools, among
other features ikaaro provides:

 - content and document management (index&search, metadata, etc.)
 - multilingual user interfaces and content
 - high level modules: wiki, forum, tracker, etc.

Changes
-------

NOTE: when upgrading to this new version run icms-update-catalog.py, a
new index has been added to fix a usability problem, and so updating
the catalog is required.

Performance improvements:
- Optimize 'get_revisions' for the root resource
- bug #605 (in progress)
- Use sprite for sort icons

User interface:
- More beautiful icons (IE6 eol)
- Users are not content (hidden from browse-content)

Features:
- folder_views: Allow to download a zip of selected files (#1189)

Access control
- #1185 User profile seen by anyone

Submodules
- Many calendar improvements and fixes (#1176, #1177, #1178, #1184)
- tracker: Add link to download a zip file with attachments

Translations
- Update French translations


